#FQ83632 - MABOS 04/10/12 - Lire le Pays du Site
Funprog LECPAYSIT(SIT)
Value Char SIT
Local Char PAYS
If SIT <>""
  If clalev([F:FCY])=0 : Local File FACILITY [FCY] : Endif
  Call LECTURE("FCY",SIT,"")  From CONTOBJ
  PAYS = [F:FCY]CRY
Endif
End PAYS

